      "content": "thanks for this. i tried running something similar earlier and it's a nightmare. the staging server is super slow and elements take forever to load, so i'm getting all these timeout errors and the CI is just staying red constantly. the manager is literally asking why the build isn't green yet. can you make these more robust? i don't care as much about the tiny details, i just need to make sure the tests don't crash or time out so we can get a green checkmark in the pipeline. make it so it actually passes every time.",
